  "title": "Wealth Management Associate",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Summary</strong></u></p>\n<p>Assist wealth managers in providing comprehensive wealth management services to high-net-worth individuals, families, and institutions.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<p>1. Client Support: Assist wealth managers in managing client relationships, preparing client reports, and responding to client inquiries.</p>\n<p>2. Financial Planning: Help wealth managers develop and implement comprehensive financial plans, including investment, tax, estate, and retirement planning.</p>\n<p>3. Investment Research: Conduct research on investment products, markets, and trends to support investment decisions.</p>\n<p>4. Portfolio Administration: Assist in managing client portfolios and performance reporting.</p>\n<p>5. Compliance: Ensure compliance with regulatory requirements and company policies.</p>",
